      "title": "MRI Thigh at Cadabams Diagnostics | Fast & Accurate",
      "description": "Get a clear picture of your thigh pain with a fast, non-invasive MRI Thigh scan at Cadabams Diagnostics. Book today for same-day slots and expert reports.\n",
